WEBVTT

00:00.105 --> 00:05.000
Shared by http://DJJ.HOME.SAPO.PT/

00:11.005 --> 00:13.737
I know. I know. I know. I'm simply exhausted.

00:14.016 --> 00:16.541
The engineers' meeting went over by about 2 1/2 hours,

00:16.773 --> 00:18.724
and of course I missed my flight,

00:18.817 --> 00:21.246
but luckily I was able to rebook the same day.

00:21.385 --> 00:22.331
Oh, you know what?

00:22.424 --> 00:24.613
Francis called, and, um,

00:24.939 --> 00:26.793
they want to publish my paper.

00:27.887 --> 00:29.887
I know. I know.

00:30.073 --> 00:32.216
Well, you know, we'll celebrate when I get home.

00:32.634 --> 00:35.206
You know what? I've got to go, sweetheart.

00:35.290 --> 00:36.626
Tell the girls I have a little something for them.

00:36.674 --> 00:39.149
Give them a kiss. All right, love you, too. Bye.

